{"title":"Wolf Tooth Adds Quick Clik Valves to EnCase Mini Pumps & Colorful Tubeless Valves","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-clik-valves-on-encase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-tubeless-valves/","date":1747332286000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_for-faster-MTB-inflation-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps &amp; colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, easier MTB inflation\" /></p>\n<p>Wolf Tooth Components goes all-in with Schwalbe’s quick-connect Clik Valve standard, adding new EnCase Pumps and colorful Tubeless Valves already set up for the new, faster &amp; easier way to air up your tires. When Schwalbe sprung the easy-to-use, easy-to-convert Clik Valve concept on us last summer, we wondered if it would gain industry traction, and whether consumers would ditch their fiddly Presta valves for another new standard. It was already easy, but now, Wolf Tooth is making it even easier to make the switch to Clik Valve.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Why Clik Valve in the first place?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps &amp; colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, up close head\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_click-to-connect-and-pump-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(All photos/Wolf Tooth)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The beauty of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/the-end-of-the-presta-valve-new-schwalbe-clik-valve-has-potential-to-become-industry-standard/\" target=\"_blank\">Clik Valve</a> is how easy it is to use. Just snap the valve cap off, click a pump onto the valve, pump away, and snap the pump head off when you are done. No more tightening or loosening the tiny nut of the end of a Presta valve, and certainly never again bending (<em>or breaking</em>) that fragile valve core when furiously pumping a tire back up on the side of the road or trail.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n<div><blockquote><div> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/C87NPfmi8ZF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\"> <div> <div></div> <div> <div></div> <div></div></div></div><div></div> <div></div><div> <div>View this post on Instagram</div></div><div></div> <div><div> <div></div> <div></div> <div></div></div><div> <div></div> <div></div></div><div> <div></div> <div></div> <div></div></div></div> <div> <div></div> <div></div></div></a><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/C87NPfmi8ZF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\">A post shared by BikeRumor (@bikerumor)</a></p></div></blockquote></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But the real secret to Clik Valve, though, is its backward compatibility. You can easily upgrade any Presta valve with a removable core, and you can still pump up a new Clik Valve equipped tire with almost any conventional Presta-ready pump. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, Schwalbe claims a 50% increase in airflow with their Hi-Flow Clik Valves compared to standard Presta cores.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Wolf Tooth Clik Valves on EnCase Pumps &amp; Tubeless Valves</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps &amp; colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, click to connect\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_holds-in-place-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Wolf Tooth EnCase Pump is now the industry’s first mini-pump to be compatible with Clik Valve. Sure, you could attach Schwalbe’s own plastic converter head to your existing mini-pump (which I did), but that just makes it stick out an extra 2.5cm, likely ruining its compact portability.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_Clik-Valve-internals-cutaway.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_Clik-Valve-internals-cutaway.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps, head details inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_Clik-Valve-internals-cutaway.webp 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_Clik-Valve-internals-cutaway-297x238.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_Clik-Valve-internals-cutaway-120x96.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_Clik-Valve-internals-cutaway-768x614.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead, WTC committed to Clik Valve by making a new set of the special pump head internals to click your valve into place, all while keeping the low profile of the original EnCase pump.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps, all sizes available\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_all-sizes-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>85cc, 40cc &amp; 30cc (<em>l-r</em>)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new EnCase Pump for Clik Valve is available in the same 3 sizes as the original EnCase minipumps and for the exact same price. The ultra compact <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-encase-30cc-smallest-pump-internal-strorage-tire-plugger/\" target=\"_blank\">30cc</a> x 120mm long and the slightly larger 40cc x 141mm long pumps sell for $65. And the biggest 85cc x 244mm long pump sells for $70.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps, repair tools tucked inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps_with-optional-tools-stored-inside-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>optional EnCase tool storage inside</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Inside, you can still hide your other <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-components-encase-system-hides-tools-inside-flat-or-drop-bars-for-easy-access/\">EnCase repair tools</a>, just like the original Presta/Shrader EnCase pumps that <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-encase-bike-pumps-with-tool-storage/\" target=\"_blank\">launched last summer.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, now in purple\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple-2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adopts-Clik-Valve-for-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valve-kit_in-purple-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Wolf Tooth Tubeless Valve Stem Kits for Clik Valve are even simpler. For $37 you get to pick either 44mm long or 60mm long alloy tubeless valves in your favorite of 9 anodized colors, and Wolf Tooth with send them to you with Clik Valve cores already installed. Technically, it’s the first chance to buy tubeless Clik Valves in colors other than black, if you didn’t just buy valves and Clik cores separately.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_without-cap.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_without-cap.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, without cap\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_without-cap.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_without-cap-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_without-cap-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_without-cap-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_with-cap.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_with-cap.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, first with colored alloy cap\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_with-cap.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_with-cap-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_with-cap-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_with-cap-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But the WTC Tubeless Clik Valves are the first to get proper matching-color anodized alloy valve caps, rather than Schwalbe’s plastic snap covers. The Wolf Tooth Clik Valve Caps also double as the Clik Valve core removal tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Plenty More Wolf Tooth Clik Valve options, as well!</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_SCHWALBE-CLIK-CORE-SET.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_SCHWALBE-CLIK-CORE-SET.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps &amp; colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, Schwalbe Clik conversion kit for Presta\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_SCHWALBE-CLIK-CORE-SET.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_SCHWALBE-CLIK-CORE-SET-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_SCHWALBE-CLIK-CORE-SET-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_SCHWALBE-CLIK-CORE-SET-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_CLIK-ADAPTER-PUMP-HEAD.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_CLIK-ADAPTER-PUMP-HEAD.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps &amp; colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, alloy pump head converter\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_CLIK-ADAPTER-PUMP-HEAD.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_CLIK-ADAPTER-PUMP-HEAD-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_CLIK-ADAPTER-PUMP-HEAD-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_CLIK-ADAPTER-PUMP-HEAD-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_ENCASE-CLIK-CONVERSION-KIT.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_ENCASE-CLIK-CONVERSION-KIT.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps, EnCase pump conversion\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_ENCASE-CLIK-CONVERSION-KIT.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_ENCASE-CLIK-CONVERSION-KIT-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_ENCASE-CLIK-CONVERSION-KIT-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_ENCASE-CLIK-CONVERSION-KIT-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Wolf Tooth also now sells the Schwalbe Clik Valve conversion kit, too. Because once you go Clik Valve on one bike, you really are going to want to do it on all your bikes. A pair of Schwalbe Hi-Flow Clik Valve Cores will set you back $12 per pair to convert one wheelset. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And of course, you’ll want to convert your floor pump tool. Wolf Tooth has a nice CNC-machined alloy Clik Valve head for $14 that simply attaches to the Schrader side of your existing pump or even a mini-inflator. Plus, if you already have one of their EnCase mini-pumps and want to convert it over to Clik Valve yourself, a $15 kit from WTC will give you the new guts to make that work in a tidy setup.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth adopts Clik Valve for EnCase mini-pumps &amp; colorful alloy Tubeless Valves, up close\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Wolf-Tooth-adds-Clik-Valves-on-EnCase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-Tubeless-Valves_on-Reserve-carbon-wheels-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All the new Wolf Tooth <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/pumps\" target=\"_blank\">Clik Valve goodies</a> are available now (<em>as are Clik Valve floor pumps from <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/lezyne-clik-valve-pumps-pocket-drive-pump-cnc-phone-mount/\" target=\"_blank\">Lezyne</a></em>).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So maybe now is the time to make the switch!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://WolfToothComponents.com\" target=\"_blank\"><em>WolfToothComponents.com</em></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-clik-valves-on-encase-mini-pumps-and-colorful-alloy-tubeless-valves/\">Wolf Tooth Adds Quick Clik Valves to EnCase Mini Pumps &amp; Colorful Tubeless Valves</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"5a65a48d296ba30537c45944e878eb9d87afdce823eae26f3191fec6f43ff8a0","category":"Cycling"}